25|$|In 2015, <b>the</b> <b>Treasury</b> <b>Secretary</b> {{announced}} that the obverse portrait of Hamilton would {{be replaced by the}} portrait of an as yet undecided woman, starting in 2020. However, due to the surging popularity of Hamilton, a hit Broadway musical based on Hamilton's life, in 2016 this decision was reversed and Hamilton will remain on the $10 bill, and instead a woman will appear on the $20 bill.|$|E
